WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.100
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.100 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 6]

01:33.520 --> 01:34.220
Leave now.

01:41.910 --> 01:43.010
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

02:12.240 --> 02:14.220
Your Highness, what brings you here?

02:19.150 --> 02:19.940
No time to explain.

02:20.240 --> 02:20.810
Run!

03:39.550 --> 03:40.220
Run!

04:08.240 --> 04:09.020
- There's an exit! - Go.

04:14.870 --> 04:15.410
Mr. Zuo,

04:15.760 --> 04:17.410
no sign of intruders in Wuxing Pavilion.

04:17.670 --> 04:18.650
All warding seals are intact,

04:18.830 --> 04:20.130
no odd spirit aura detected.

04:21.150 --> 04:22.180
That green light

04:22.760 --> 04:24.180
is the Divine Tree's aura.

04:24.590 --> 04:26.540
I definitely got it right.

04:29.270 --> 04:29.810
Mr. Zuo!

04:31.320 --> 04:31.890
Mr. Zuo!

04:33.270 --> 04:34.300
What's going on?

04:34.520 --> 04:35.420
Who broke in?

04:35.640 --> 04:36.180
Jiaping,

04:36.760 --> 04:39.210
are you carrying the key to the Futu Tower?

04:39.320 --> 04:39.740
Yes,

04:42.560 --> 04:43.740
I've kept it with me at all times.

04:47.270 --> 04:48.660
The tower is wrapped in heavy restriction spells.

04:49.270 --> 04:50.370
Anyone breaking in without the key

04:50.830 --> 04:51.980
will trigger alarms.

05:07.000 --> 05:09.100
I slept dead to the world last night

05:09.200 --> 05:10.660
and didn't feel anything off.

05:16.590 --> 05:17.980
None of the restriction spells around

05:18.470 --> 05:19.890
are cracked or loose.

05:20.760 --> 05:22.660
Was the intruder strong enough

05:23.230 --> 05:24.620
to come through solid rock?

05:27.120 --> 05:27.690
Or

05:28.080 --> 05:29.810
hidden paths we don't know about?

05:32.230 --> 05:32.940
I'll search again.

05:38.960 --> 05:39.420
Mr. Zuo,

05:40.080 --> 05:41.940
my master, Elder Xuanshan, said

05:42.350 --> 05:43.570
the Divine Tree disappeared

05:43.680 --> 05:45.660
after the Sea Calamity ages ago.

05:48.270 --> 05:49.420
It hasn't been seen

05:50.880 --> 05:52.690
in the past five centuries.

05:54.760 --> 05:55.370
Seems bad things

05:56.710 --> 05:58.940
are coming to this academy.

06:07.830 --> 06:08.810
Don't you remember

06:09.200 --> 06:10.450
what happened back then?

06:13.320 --> 06:14.890
I was training with The Record of Spirit Release.

06:16.320 --> 06:17.860
I pulled in some spirit energy,

06:18.910 --> 06:20.330
but messed up the technique.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.130
I can't remember clearly.

06:23.470 --> 06:24.060
Xiuyuan,

06:24.320 --> 06:25.250
did you see anything?

06:27.910 --> 06:29.810
Your aura was unstable,

06:30.270 --> 06:30.980
and you lacked spirit power,

06:31.520 --> 06:32.940
so I tried to stabilize your spirit aura.

06:34.440 --> 06:36.770
Then a blast of power knocked me flying.

06:41.520 --> 06:43.860
Any pain anywhere?

06:45.710 --> 06:46.250
Or

06:46.910 --> 06:47.940
feel any different at all?

06:51.270 --> 06:51.890
Nothing.

06:53.910 --> 06:55.250
I don't feel any different at all.

06:56.790 --> 06:58.210
Could we have triggered

06:59.350 --> 07:00.330
some ancient restriction spells?

07:02.000 --> 07:03.370
There are countless ancient books.

07:03.590 --> 07:04.690
Runes cover shelves

07:04.710 --> 07:05.540
and floors alike.

07:05.560 --> 07:06.500
We never know what we touched.

07:08.270 --> 07:09.450
Leave other matters aside.

07:09.790 --> 07:11.210
The trouble at the Script Tower has blown up.

07:11.520 --> 07:12.980
What if our teachers question us?

07:14.120 --> 07:15.420
If the Disciplinary Pavilion finds out,

07:15.640 --> 07:16.770
we'll face harsh punishment.

07:17.560 --> 07:18.330
We might

07:18.640 --> 07:19.740
get expelled from the academy.

07:26.350 --> 07:27.130
Have you heard?

07:27.800 --> 07:29.130
Someone broke into the Futu Tower last night.

07:29.480 --> 07:30.170
The Futu Tower?

07:30.270 --> 07:31.250
Can't believe that it happened.

07:31.270 --> 07:31.770
Indeed.

07:42.270 --> 07:43.500
Xiuyuan, Lifei,

07:44.560 --> 07:45.060
come here.

07:45.710 --> 07:46.130
Come here.

07:48.270 --> 07:49.450
This is Yue Cailing,

07:49.470 --> 07:50.980
favored disciple of Immortal Guangwei

07:51.000 --> 07:52.500
from the Wuyue Court.

07:54.640 --> 07:56.940
This is Qin Yangling,

07:57.150 --> 07:58.620
chief disciple of Elder Cuixuan.

08:02.520 --> 08:04.330
My master, Immortal Guangwei, has heard

08:04.350 --> 08:05.540
of Lei's extraordinary talent.

08:05.910 --> 08:07.740
He sent me here with an offer.

08:11.350 --> 08:13.370
Once you finish your studies,

08:13.760 --> 08:15.250
would you like to cultivate at the Wuyue Court?

08:18.880 --> 08:19.860
Thanks for the kind offer.

08:20.150 --> 08:22.210
But I've only been here for less than a month,

08:22.590 --> 08:23.660
so I need more time to cultivate.

08:25.710 --> 08:27.180
I've got things to do. I'm leaving.

08:28.000 --> 08:28.370
Wait.

08:30.030 --> 08:30.940
No, he…

08:32.030 --> 08:34.010
He's just quiet and bad with words.

08:34.230 --> 08:35.620
Deep down, he'd love to go.

08:35.640 --> 08:36.490
Absolutely.

08:38.870 --> 08:41.180
The immortal sects shall select a year later.

08:41.510 --> 08:42.970
Why recruit this early?

08:48.440 --> 08:50.260
The academy's Futu Tower was broken in.

08:50.750 --> 08:52.730
It houses ancient books from all immortal sects across the nine states.

08:53.080 --> 08:53.970
This is extremely critical,

08:54.440 --> 08:55.780
so we merely came to help.

09:00.160 --> 09:00.690
Xiuyuan.

09:01.630 --> 09:02.780
Zong Quan is here again.

09:56.680 --> 09:59.940
Last night, someone snuck into the forbidden Futu Tower.

10:01.280 --> 10:02.690
If any of you did,

10:03.960 --> 10:05.180
step forward voluntarily.

10:09.350 --> 10:10.490
I'd never dare to do such a thing!

10:10.510 --> 10:11.730
No thief would stick around afterward.

10:11.750 --> 10:12.450
Who was it?

10:13.470 --> 10:14.690
- Don't drag everyone down! - Yes.

10:20.960 --> 10:21.490
What?

10:22.440 --> 10:23.780
None of you dares admit?

10:28.440 --> 10:28.940
Jiaping.

10:41.960 --> 10:42.540
You'll handle this.

10:52.710 --> 10:54.970
Since none of you admit it,

10:55.680 --> 10:59.020
I'll have the script spirits in the tower to identify the intruder.

12:14.990 --> 12:16.260
The script spirits found

12:16.440 --> 12:18.780
no trace of the tower aura on any disciple.

12:22.160 --> 12:23.210
In this case,

12:24.320 --> 12:26.260
the intruder can't be one of our academy.

12:31.200 --> 12:34.690
Alright, you may all disperse.

12:35.800 --> 12:36.540
Wait a moment.

12:43.200 --> 12:46.540
Strange spirit aura lingered above the Futu Tower,

12:46.920 --> 12:48.970
most likely related to the Sea Calamity.

12:49.830 --> 12:51.690
It concerns the safety of the nine states.

12:52.280 --> 12:53.730
How can you brush it off so lightly?

12:55.510 --> 12:58.140
What do you want to do, Mr. Zong?

13:00.830 --> 13:04.450
The Longming Sanctuary's treasure, Spirit-searching Branch,

13:05.110 --> 13:07.810
is capable of tracking rare spirit auras.

13:08.510 --> 13:10.850
I'd like to give it a try.

13:46.590 --> 13:48.020
Oh, no! I'm exposed.

14:13.990 --> 14:14.900
You again!

14:18.400 --> 14:19.730
Meet your end!

14:24.160 --> 14:24.690
Xiuyuan!

14:34.960 --> 14:35.660
Xiuyuan!

14:40.320 --> 14:41.180
You're seeking death!

15:30.680 --> 15:31.380
Xiuyuan!

15:38.080 --> 15:39.020
Mr. Zong!

15:44.750 --> 15:45.900
- Xiuyuan! - Xiuyuan!

15:46.320 --> 15:47.210
Lifei, are you alright?

15:58.680 --> 15:59.490
What was I thinking?

16:00.800 --> 16:01.940
Had Mr. Zuo not intervened,

16:02.680 --> 16:04.330
I would've sacrificed myself to save Lifei.

16:07.470 --> 16:09.970
Mr. Zuo is said to be the top hidden cultivator across the nine states.

16:10.560 --> 16:11.730
Your power is truly unfathomable.

16:15.160 --> 16:15.780
Zuo Qiu,

16:16.870 --> 16:17.690
you were

16:17.990 --> 16:20.900
close friends with that traitor cultivator years ago.

16:21.470 --> 16:22.610
Since this spirit aura has resurfaced,

16:22.870 --> 16:24.450
your academy cannot escape blame.

16:24.990 --> 16:28.060
That man once led us to fight the Sea Calamity.

16:28.440 --> 16:30.330
The Longming Sanctuary took the hardest hit,

16:30.680 --> 16:32.090
so you shared a deep connection.

16:33.110 --> 16:35.260
Mr. Zong, do not make excuses

16:35.590 --> 16:36.570
to hurt my students.

16:38.800 --> 16:39.730
Are they students?

16:40.280 --> 16:41.610
They are murderers, obviously.

16:42.230 --> 16:42.570
You!

16:42.590 --> 16:45.380
He alone slew several of my disciples.

16:45.750 --> 16:47.420
All of them are his accomplices.

16:49.160 --> 16:51.900
I shall take them back

16:52.160 --> 16:54.020
to offer sacrifice for my fallen disciples.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.380
Bah!

16:56.400 --> 16:58.300
The Longming Sanctuary aided the wicked.

16:58.320 --> 16:59.300
Cruel and heartless,

16:59.470 --> 17:01.180
you ravaged Gaolu and slaughtered its people.

17:01.560 --> 17:03.850
Yeah, besides Xiuyuan,

17:04.230 --> 17:06.850
Gelin, Changyue and I

17:07.230 --> 17:08.940
are all survivors of Gaolu.

17:09.270 --> 17:10.140
We've scraped by

17:10.640 --> 17:12.620
all these years just to stay alive,

17:13.160 --> 17:13.940
yet you

17:14.550 --> 17:16.100
still hunt us without end.

17:16.510 --> 17:19.210
Countless cultivators walk this world.

17:20.230 --> 17:22.490
Shall your baseless words

17:22.680 --> 17:25.180
brand the Longming Sanctuary as killers?

17:28.440 --> 17:29.970
That day at the Yange Hall in Lugong Town,

17:30.270 --> 17:31.530
your disciples burst in suddenly

17:31.550 --> 17:32.730
and tried to take my life.

17:33.160 --> 17:34.660
As a senior of the immortal sects,

17:35.160 --> 17:37.140
you ordered your disciples to wield immortal arts recklessly

17:37.160 --> 17:37.940
and slay the innocent.

17:38.920 --> 17:40.050
Xiuyuan and the others only defended themselves.

17:40.750 --> 17:41.490
What's wrong with that?

17:47.440 --> 17:51.730
As the immortal sect protecting Wugou,

17:51.880 --> 17:54.050
we only followed orders to wipe out rebels.

17:54.400 --> 17:56.250
Rebels all deserve to die.

17:56.270 --> 17:58.450
Are you out of your mind?

17:59.070 --> 18:00.380
They were just kids seven years ago.

18:00.400 --> 18:01.490
How were they rebels?

18:02.160 --> 18:02.820
Moreover,

18:03.230 --> 18:05.010
they lived fine on their own land,

18:05.030 --> 18:05.940
but you took their territory

18:05.960 --> 18:06.860
and called them rebels.

18:06.920 --> 18:08.180
Using your logic, cops should arrest

18:08.200 --> 18:09.490
homeowners instead of thieves!

18:11.710 --> 18:12.420
Plus,

18:13.120 --> 18:15.450
your top disciples,

18:16.070 --> 18:17.210
picked on regular people,

18:17.230 --> 18:18.250
only to get killed by them.

18:18.710 --> 18:19.730
If I were you,

18:19.960 --> 18:21.250
I'd have hidden this embarrassment forever.

18:21.440 --> 18:22.380
How shameless!

18:25.470 --> 18:27.100
Still arguing nonsense.

18:27.600 --> 18:29.290
The Spirit-searching Branch

18:29.510 --> 18:31.050
pointed right at you before it broke.

18:31.400 --> 18:33.490
The strange aura over the Futu Tower

18:33.710 --> 18:34.580
must have something to do with you.

18:35.200 --> 18:35.530
I...

18:37.070 --> 18:39.140
Zuo Qiu, can't you see

18:39.230 --> 18:40.100
what's really happening?

18:46.960 --> 18:47.690
Mr. Zong,

18:49.440 --> 18:51.290
they've not been in the academy long

18:51.680 --> 18:52.580
and aren't strong enough

18:53.120 --> 18:55.180
to get past the restriction spells in the Futu Tower.

18:55.600 --> 18:57.620
We need to look into this properly.

18:57.880 --> 18:59.730
Don't convict them right away.

19:02.750 --> 19:03.450
Very well.

19:03.790 --> 19:05.940
I shall stay here

19:06.200 --> 19:07.450
and await your word.

19:15.230 --> 19:15.820
Alright.

19:16.680 --> 19:18.490
This matter ends for today.

19:19.440 --> 19:20.530
Everyone, disperse.

19:32.960 --> 19:33.530
Elder Zhu,

19:35.920 --> 19:38.050
take Lei Xiuyuan to heal his wounds.

19:39.600 --> 19:40.010
Understood.

20:00.550 --> 20:03.690
Zong Quan's Golden Light Formation stabs deep to the core,

20:04.160 --> 20:06.010
yet it should not hurt you this severely.

20:09.920 --> 20:11.690
Why didn't you resist with your spirit power?

20:18.200 --> 20:19.140
Xiuyuan

20:20.440 --> 20:21.820
gave me all his spirit power.

20:24.880 --> 20:26.900
No wonder you were untouched

20:27.640 --> 20:29.250
amid the golden light.

20:32.120 --> 20:33.900
He risked his own life for you.

20:34.680 --> 20:35.820
Such a youthful bond

20:35.840 --> 20:36.940
is truly precious.

20:37.680 --> 20:39.340
I shall prepare the medicine.

20:46.710 --> 20:47.730
What were you thinking

20:48.200 --> 20:49.050
when you saved me?

20:52.790 --> 20:53.770
Nothing at all.

20:56.550 --> 20:57.340
Were you not afraid of dying?

20:58.600 --> 20:59.140
I was.

21:02.880 --> 21:06.340
But Zong Quan never intended to spare me.

21:08.680 --> 21:12.820
Better one perishes than both.

21:15.550 --> 21:16.420
I passed my power to you,

21:17.680 --> 21:18.820
and you could seek out your master.

21:19.710 --> 21:20.580
Life is harsh;

21:23.120 --> 21:24.340
at least you could fulfill your wish.

21:36.360 --> 21:38.290
Lifei, where are you going?

21:39.160 --> 21:40.340
To demand justice from our teachers.

21:47.200 --> 21:48.340
Xiuyuan, how do you feel?

21:53.200 --> 21:53.770
Mr. Zhu,

21:54.880 --> 21:56.050
how is Xiuyuan's injury?

21:56.400 --> 21:57.210
What can we do to help?

21:57.750 --> 21:58.860
His meridians are damaged.

21:59.470 --> 22:01.250
Someone must channel spirit power into him nonstop.

22:01.710 --> 22:02.250
I volunteer!

22:03.230 --> 22:04.210
We all do.

22:06.120 --> 22:06.730
Xiuyuan,

22:07.470 --> 22:08.940
you've endured countless hardships,

22:09.120 --> 22:10.530
yet your friends

22:10.790 --> 22:11.940
treat you with all their hearts.

22:12.550 --> 22:14.340
Hard times will surely give way to good fortune.

22:18.230 --> 22:18.860
Thank you.

22:19.710 --> 22:22.100
We owe you thanks.

22:22.640 --> 22:23.420
We only wish

22:23.750 --> 22:24.970
you'd stop worrying over us from now on.

22:25.960 --> 22:27.860
Whether it's the Longming Sanctuary or Zong Quan,

22:28.550 --> 22:29.450
we'll stand together.

22:31.470 --> 22:32.140
Alright.

22:33.550 --> 22:35.290
Though Zong Quan rules an immortal sect,

22:36.120 --> 22:38.770
he's petty and cruel.

22:39.120 --> 22:40.380
You slew his disciples

22:40.550 --> 22:41.940
and he'll never let you off easily.

22:42.200 --> 22:43.660
Steer clear of him,

22:44.310 --> 22:45.450
and never face him alone.

22:46.600 --> 22:48.250
That strange aura is the Divine Tree.

22:48.990 --> 22:49.690
Yes.

22:51.070 --> 22:53.580
The Divine Tree absorbing heaven and earth's spirit energy

22:54.200 --> 22:55.900
has been lost for hundreds of years, right?

22:56.400 --> 22:58.180
Zong Quan came to the academy

22:58.470 --> 22:59.820
just to hunt for the Divine Tree.

23:00.470 --> 23:01.450
Do not engage him

23:02.030 --> 23:02.810
[Xuanshanzi, Xingzheng Hall]

23:02.810 --> 23:04.140
in direct conflict unless necessary.

23:09.920 --> 23:11.530
Are you alright?

23:12.440 --> 23:14.770
I'm fine, just an old wound.

23:15.230 --> 23:18.100
The Sea Calamity draws near; time waits for none.

23:18.750 --> 23:20.820
The Divine Tree holds Yue's fate.

23:21.200 --> 23:23.180
Find out where it is at once.

23:28.600 --> 23:29.290
Mr. Zuo,

23:29.750 --> 23:30.770
Zong Quan is hunting

23:30.790 --> 23:32.450
Xiuyuan and me.

23:32.920 --> 23:34.420
You have to protect us.

23:43.750 --> 23:44.250
Sit.

23:48.230 --> 23:50.770
Did many spirits

23:51.360 --> 23:53.490
draw near you in Qingqiu?

23:56.600 --> 23:57.900
Besides,

23:59.120 --> 24:02.690
when I traveled with my master,

24:03.310 --> 24:05.340
all kinds of spirits

24:05.710 --> 24:07.290
often lingered around me.

24:07.680 --> 24:08.900
My master warned me repeatedly

24:09.120 --> 24:10.660
never to tell others.

24:13.750 --> 24:14.420
Mr. Zuo,

24:15.990 --> 24:17.250
will something bad happen to me?

24:21.230 --> 24:23.450
After a tiring day, you must be hungry.

24:25.640 --> 24:26.690
Have a green bean cake.

24:31.230 --> 24:32.970
My master loved these too.

24:36.120 --> 24:36.730
Yes.

24:37.600 --> 24:39.050
We elders

24:39.510 --> 24:41.050
all fancy sweet treats.

24:43.400 --> 24:46.050
You know my master,

24:46.360 --> 24:46.900
don't you?

24:50.360 --> 24:53.770
Since your master sent you here,

24:54.960 --> 24:56.420
stay here in peace.

24:57.360 --> 24:58.820
The academy will shield you

24:59.270 --> 25:02.340
as long as you stay here.

25:04.750 --> 25:06.860
The strange aura from the Futu Tower

25:07.120 --> 25:08.050
must be related to you.

25:09.310 --> 25:11.900
Zuo Qiu, are you too blind and foolish

25:12.120 --> 25:12.970
to see this?

25:13.600 --> 25:14.180
Mr. Zuo.

25:17.640 --> 25:21.290
Lifei, trust your master's arrangements.

25:21.960 --> 25:23.210
Some truths are better left unknown

25:23.920 --> 25:25.250
for your own good.

25:36.640 --> 25:39.010
What did Mr. Zuo say? Will he protect us?

25:39.310 --> 25:40.100
Smart boy.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.970
He wants us

25:42.120 --> 25:43.490
to stay inside the academy

25:43.510 --> 25:44.180
and never step out.

25:44.550 --> 25:45.530
He's right.

25:46.120 --> 25:47.420
If we stay here,

25:47.790 --> 25:48.770
Zong Quan

25:49.070 --> 25:50.250
won't dare act recklessly.

25:54.550 --> 25:56.530
The Divine Tree holds Yue's fate.

25:56.960 --> 25:59.100
Find out where it is at once.

26:01.550 --> 26:02.140
Lifei,

26:03.070 --> 26:05.380
when you entered the Futu Tower with Xiuyuan,

26:05.640 --> 26:07.490
did you spot anything resembling the Divine Tree?

26:09.990 --> 26:10.530
The Divine Tree?

26:11.710 --> 26:12.690
Why ask that suddenly?

26:13.440 --> 26:16.250
Xuanshanzi said the strange spirit aura in the academy

26:17.550 --> 26:18.290
is the Divine Tree.

26:20.550 --> 26:22.290
Then it has nothing to do with me.

26:23.400 --> 26:24.530
There's no such tree,

26:24.550 --> 26:25.420
nothing but books inside.

26:25.920 --> 26:26.820
If I'd found the Divine Tree,

26:26.840 --> 26:27.860
I wouldn't have feared Zong Quan.

26:28.550 --> 26:29.380
Makes sense.

26:32.470 --> 26:33.820
No matter what Zong Quan's plan is,

26:34.200 --> 26:34.940
our top priority

26:35.840 --> 26:37.900
is passing the monthly exam to stay here.

26:40.120 --> 26:42.180
Set aside the Divine Tree matter for now.

26:54.230 --> 26:55.420
This is the book from the Futu Tower.

27:06.200 --> 27:08.180
Let's start studying The Record of Spirit Release.

27:08.200 --> 27:09.100
Come on, let's go.

27:15.270 --> 27:17.100
This is my room.

27:17.990 --> 27:20.100
Don't worry, heal your wounds.

27:20.270 --> 27:21.340
We won't disturb you.

27:22.710 --> 27:23.620
- Wait. - Right.

27:24.400 --> 27:26.180
This is ambergris.

27:26.270 --> 27:27.580
Drink it with water,

27:27.790 --> 27:29.450
and it'll greatly aid our cultivation.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.660
Really?

27:31.270 --> 27:31.860
Let's go.

27:31.880 --> 27:32.900
- Go. - Get some right now.

28:13.840 --> 28:15.100
She's no ordinary orphan girl.

28:16.160 --> 28:17.180
After all these twists,

28:17.920 --> 28:19.450
could there truly be some fate binding us?

28:21.790 --> 28:23.940
I was reckless in the hall today,

28:25.160 --> 28:27.380
yet it lowered her guard at least.

28:29.160 --> 28:31.250
But Zong Quan lurks as a new threat,

28:32.510 --> 28:33.420
how to break this deadlock?

28:46.790 --> 28:47.730
Master.

28:47.750 --> 28:48.970
My heart's racing wildly.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.580
What's wrong with me?

28:51.160 --> 28:52.490
Wait for me.

28:54.200 --> 28:55.450
Master.

29:43.680 --> 29:46.050
Mr. Mo, Lifei seeks an audience.

29:53.790 --> 29:54.340
Come in.

30:30.120 --> 30:32.010
Mr. Mo, what spirit art is this?

30:32.680 --> 30:33.490
The Yearning Bond.

30:38.640 --> 30:40.420
So you are missing someone.

30:56.400 --> 30:57.250
What brings you here?

30:57.880 --> 30:59.420
I heard you excel at crafting artifacts,

30:59.440 --> 31:00.660
so I've come to ask

31:01.310 --> 31:03.050
if there is any artifact

31:03.710 --> 31:05.940
that can sense another's safety instantly,

31:06.120 --> 31:07.380
and show exactly where they are.

31:13.400 --> 31:14.210
For Lei Xiuyuan?

31:22.200 --> 31:22.970
There is such an artifact,

31:23.880 --> 31:26.490
but it only works if two people share

31:26.790 --> 31:27.580
sincere mutual affection.

31:28.440 --> 31:30.820
What matters is the people, not the artifact.

31:31.600 --> 31:32.620
Only two?

31:33.360 --> 31:34.420
That's far too few.

31:36.200 --> 31:37.010
Make it for three.

31:38.030 --> 31:38.690
Three?

31:41.680 --> 31:43.380
Besides Lei Xiuyuan, who else?

31:43.510 --> 31:44.420
Ji Tongzhou.

31:45.120 --> 31:47.340
We're like brothers, bound by unbreakable loyalty.

31:50.070 --> 31:51.340
The other day in the great hall,

31:51.790 --> 31:53.380
you risked your lives to shield one another.

31:54.160 --> 31:56.290
Such devotion is truly touching.

31:59.030 --> 31:59.490
Very well,

32:00.680 --> 32:01.490
I agree.

32:02.230 --> 32:05.420
Yet crafting this artifact will take time.

32:07.030 --> 32:08.770
But the monthly exam is almost here.

32:10.200 --> 32:13.660
Can you finish it in three days?

32:17.200 --> 32:18.250
Three days?

32:21.030 --> 32:23.100
I've read over a thousand storybooks,

32:23.680 --> 32:25.490
knowing all about lovers,

32:25.510 --> 32:26.490
mortal and immortal alike.

32:27.710 --> 32:28.940
I'm very familiar with the Matchmaker.

32:29.600 --> 32:31.620
No matter who your beloved is,

32:32.200 --> 32:33.940
I'll make sure fate ties you two together.

32:44.070 --> 32:45.010
Fine, three days it is.

33:01.440 --> 33:02.340
What part don't you get?

33:11.750 --> 33:13.730
When you first start Qi refining, train lung energy first.

33:13.990 --> 33:19.660
Breathe leisurely, evenly, faintly, long and softly.

33:19.960 --> 33:20.730
That's what it means.

33:30.840 --> 33:32.940
Your Ladyship, these are the newly copied cultivation notes.

33:34.070 --> 33:34.690
You're blocking my view.

33:34.960 --> 33:37.860
Move aside. You're blocking my view.

33:39.510 --> 33:40.490
So annoying.

33:45.990 --> 33:46.940
Tongzhou.

34:53.550 --> 34:54.220
What's this?

34:56.440 --> 34:56.900
This…

34:58.760 --> 35:00.650
Powerful spirit artifacts bear their own names.

35:02.070 --> 35:04.570
This place is Qianxiang room.

35:09.150 --> 35:09.970
Then

35:14.150 --> 35:16.940
this will be our exclusive artifact,

35:17.320 --> 35:18.970
the Eternal Fragrance.

35:23.670 --> 35:24.130
Sounds good.

35:43.890 --> 35:46.850
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

35:46.970 --> 35:49.610
♪I'll never back down♪

35:49.650 --> 35:55.160
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

35:55.880 --> 35:59.640
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

35:59.760 --> 36:02.720
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

36:02.880 --> 36:07.560
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

36:07.720 --> 36:12.080
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

36:12.080 --> 36:14.560
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

36:14.680 --> 36:20.200
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

36:20.600 --> 36:23.150
♪Banners wave, war drums thunder across the sky♪

36:23.150 --> 36:24.740
Let's test if it works.

36:24.740 --> 36:26.760
♪Sing everlasting verses♪

36:26.880 --> 36:32.360
♪A youth without passion is all in vain♪

36:33.360 --> 36:36.320
