40:00.920 --> 40:01.450
Tongzhou.

40:07.240 --> 40:08.610
Capture your black piece,

40:08.630 --> 40:09.570
and we'll win.

40:22.800 --> 40:23.970
The Chaos Stone stirs strangely.

40:25.760 --> 40:26.420
What's happening?

40:51.110 --> 40:51.650
Xiuyuan!

40:55.280 --> 40:55.860
Xiuyuan!

41:27.760 --> 41:28.420
Be careful!

41:28.440 --> 41:29.220
I'll hold off Zong Quan.

42:08.470 --> 42:09.050
Xiuyuan!

42:42.200 --> 42:42.920
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.920 --> 42:44.720
